          "candidate_value": "A $5 fee applies for each pre-authorized debit, cash withdrawals, and transfers made in branch or with a Telephone Banking associate.",
          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-ab3df22296dd159e",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "What are the fees for the Savings Builder Account?\nThe good news is that there are no monthly fees for the Savings Builder Account, however there are transaction fees. You get one debit transaction per month, at no cost *23 with the Savings Builder Account and then a $5 fee for each withdrawal or additional transfer out that month *25 .\nWhat are the fees for the BMO Savings Amplifier Account? The Savings Amplifier Account includes a $0 monthly plan fee, a $0 minimum opening deposit, and no fees on any self-serve transfers to your other BMO accounts. A $5 fee applies for each pre-authorized debit, cash withdrawals, and transfers made in branch or with a Telephone Banking associate.",
